f=\"/message/\"><li class=\"l-header-nav--item\"><span>社長挨拶</span></li></a>\n          <a href=\"/environment/\"><li class=\"l-header-nav--item\"><span>環境への取り組み</span></li></a>\n          <a href=\"/datasheet/\"><li class=\"l-header-nav--item\"><span>安全データシート</span></li></a>\n                    <a href=\"/#service\"><li class=\"l-header-nav--item\"><span>取扱い商品</span></li></a>\n                    <a href=\"/info/\"><li class=\"l-header-nav--item\"><span>お知らせ</span></li></a>\n          <a href=\"/recruit/\"><li class=\"l-header-nav--item\"><span>採用情報</span></li></a>\n        </ul>\n        <a href=\"/contact/\"><div class=\"l-header-contact\"><img src=\"https://nagoya-sanso.co.jp/wp-content/themes/nagoya-sanso/images/mail_icon_white.png\"></div></a>\n      </header>\n  <div class=\"c-page\">\n    <section class=\"c-page-visual\">\n      <picture>\n        <source media=\"(max-width: 767px)\" srcset=\"https://nagoya-sanso.co.jp/wp-content/themes/nagoya-sanso/images/sp/recruit_detail_visual.jpg\">\n        <img src=\"https://nagoya-sanso.co.jp/wp-content/themes/nagoya-sanso/images/recruit_detail_visual.jpg\">\n      </picture>\n      <div class=\"c-page-container\">\n        <div class=\"c-page-ttl\">\n          <div class=\"u-font-en c-page-ttl__main\">RECRUIT</div>\n          <div class=\"c-page-ttl__sub\"><h1>募集要項</h1></div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"c-page-breadcrumbs\"><a href=\"/\">NAGOYA SANSO HOME</a><span class=\"c-page-breadcrumbs__arrow\">></span><a href=\"/recruit/\">採用情報</a><span class=\"c-page-breadcrumbs__arrow\">></span>募集要項</div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"p-recruit_detail\">\n      <section class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap\">\n        <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--icon\"><img src=\"https://nagoya-sanso.co.jp/wp-content/themes/nagoya-sanso/images/indust_ttl.png\"></picture>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--ttl u-font-en\">Sales</div>\n        <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--subttl\">営業スタッフ</div>\n        <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--conts\">\n                      <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__head\">業務内容</div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__cont\">正社員（期間の定めなし）<br />\r\n既存取引先に対する提案販売（ルートセールス）<br />\r\n・溶接関連の消耗材料類の販売<br />\r\n・溶接機、溶接ロボットの販売及び据付等</div>\n            </div>\n                                <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__head\">応募資格</div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__cont\">高卒以上、普通自動車免許</div>\n            </div>\n                                <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__head\">給　　与</div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__cont\">月給　２１０，０００円　以上<br />\r\n※年齢・経験・能力を考慮の上決定（当社規定による）</div>\n            </div>\n                                <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__head\">待　　遇</div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__cont\">昇給　年１回<br />\r\n賞与　年２回（前年実績／４ヶ月分）<br />\r\n各種手当（通勤手当（上限５０，０００円）・職務手当・家族手当・住宅手当・営業手当・皆勤手当・残業手当他）<br />\r\n社会保険（健康保険・厚生年金・雇用保険・労災保険）<br />\r\n退職金制度（勤続５年以上）</div>\n            </div>\n                                <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__head\">福利厚生</div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__cont\">財形貯蓄制度・保養施設</div>\n            </div>\n                                <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__head\">諸制度</div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__cont\">育児休業制度・介護休業制度・育児時短勤務制度・介護時短勤務制度等</div>\n            </div>\n                                <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__head\">時　　間</div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__cont\">８：３０～１７：１５（実働７時間４５分）</div>\n            </div>\n                                <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__head\">休日・休暇</div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__cont\">土曜日・日曜日・祝日<br />\r\n夏季休暇（５日以上）・年末年始休暇（６日以上）<br />\r\n年次有給休暇・特別休暇（慶事・弔事他）</div>\n            </div>\n                                <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__head\">勤務地</div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__cont\">愛知県（岡崎市）・三重県（桑名市）・茨城県<br />\r\n※転居を伴う転勤はありません</div>\n            </div>\n                                <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__head\">その他</div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-wrap--item__cont\">マイカー通勤可（駐車場完備）<br />\r\n試用期間あり（入社３ヶ月）※待遇の変更はありません<br />\r\n◆未経験者でも歓迎いたします<br />\r\n◆詳細はお気軽にお問合せ下さい</div>\n            </div>\n                  </div><? //.p-recruit_detail-wrap--conts ?>\n        <div class=\"c-btn p-recruit_detail-btn\"><a href=\"/recruit/\" class=\"c-btn__hover\"><div class=\"c-btn__text c-gas-btn__text\">採用情報へ戻る</div></a></div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"p-recruit_detail-contact\">\n        <div class=\"l-container\">\n          <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-contact--icon\"><img src=\"https://nagoya-sanso.co.jp/wp-content/themes/nagoya-sanso/images/lets_join.png\"></div>\n          <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-contact--ttl u-font-en\">ENTRY FORM</div>\n          <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-contact--subttl\">エントリーフォーム</div>\n          <div class=\"p-recruit_detail-contact--wrap\">\n            <div class=\"c-steps\">\n              <div class=\"c-step c-step__here\">\n                <div class=\"u-font-en\">STEP1</div>\n                <div class=\"c-step--desc\">入力</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"c-step\">\n                <div class=\"u-font-en\">STEP2</div>\n                <div class=\"c-step--desc\">確認</div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"c-step\">\n                <div class=\"u-font-en\">STEP3</div>\n                <div class=\"c-step--desc\">完了</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"h-adr\">\n              <div id=\"mw_wp_form_mw-wp-form-72\" class=\"mw_wp_form mw_wp_form_input  \">\n\t\t\t\t\t<form method=\"post\" action=\"\" enctype=\"multipart/form-data\"><p><span class=\"p-country-name\" style=\"display: none;\">Japan</span></p>\n<table class=\"c-form\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"c-form-tr\">\n<td class=\"c-form-must\">必須</td>\n<th class=\"c-form-th\">業種</th>\n<td class=\"c-form-field\">\n<select name=\"industry\" >\n\t\t\t<option value=\"--- 選択してください\" >\n\t\t\t--- 選択してください\t\t</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"営業スタッフ\" >\n\t\t\t営業スタッフ\t\t</option>\n\t</select>\n\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"__children[industry][]\" value=\"{&quot;--- \\u9078\\u629e\\u3057\\u3066\\u304f\\u3060\\u3055\\u3044&quot;:&quot;--- \\u9078\\u629e\\u3057\\u3066\\u304f\\u3060\\u3055\\u3044&quot;,&quot;\\u55b6\\u696d\\u30b9\\u30bf\\u30c3\\u30d5&quot;:&quot;\\u55b6\\u696d\\u30b9\\u30bf\\u30c3\\u30d5&quot;}\" />\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"c-form-tr\">\n<td class=\"c-form-must\">必須</td>\n<th class=\"c-form-th\">お名前</th>\n<td class=\"c-form-field\">\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" size=\"60\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"名古屋太郎\" />\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"c-form-tr c-form-tr__yubin\">\n<td class=\"c-form-must\">必須</td>\n<th class=\"c-form-th\">住所</th>\n<td class=\"c-form-field c-form-yubin\"><span class=\"c-form-yubin--icon\">〒</span>\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"zip\" class=\"p-postal-code\" size=\"60\" value=\"\" placeholder=\"4550801\" />\n<span class=\"c-form-yubin--note\">（入力で住所検索できます）</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"c-form-tr\">\n<td class=\"c-form-field\">\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"ad